 </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Quick Answer — liftable -->
 <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-concrete py-12">
 <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
 <aside class="border border-hairline bg-gold-500/5 p-7">
 <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-700">Quick Answer</p>
 <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal sm:text-xl">Bighorn Threads screen-prints custom apparel for Las Vegas construction crews and contractors — plastisol, water-based, discharge, and FR-safe inks, all Pantone-matched in-house. The minimum is 24 pieces, up to 8 colors on the manual press (12 on auto), with rush options on most jobs. We print tees, hoodies, hi-vis polyester, and FR shirts using arc-rated inks that preserve the rating.</p>
 </aside>
 </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Process — concrete -->
 <section class="bg-concrete py-20 sm:py-24">
