 </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Garments + Minimums — concrete -->
 <section class="bg-concrete py-20 sm:py-24">
 <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
 <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
 <div>
 <p class="kicker mb-3">Garments</p>
 <h2 class="mb-4 font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal sm:text-4xl">What we print on.</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ash">
 Cotton through synthetics. Decorate-able workwear. We carry the brands trades actually wear — Carhartt, Dickies, Bulwark, Port Authority, ML Kishigo.
 </p>
 <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
 {garments.map((g) => (
