 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal transition-colors group-hover:text-gold-600">Rush Orders</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">rush turnaround on most jobs. 48 for repeat clients.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/blog/screen-printing-vs-embroidery-construction/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
